---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Symbiotic Licence NFT - ResonantOS" description="The Symbiotic Licence NFT is a DAO-issued non-transferable credential for ResonantOS licence and co-ownership rights.">
	<section class="px-4 pb-16 pt-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
			<p class="mb-5 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">Symbiotic Licence</p>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">A licence credential for Community Members.</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-8 text-zinc-300">
				The Symbiotic Licence NFT records a wallet's licence and co-ownership commitment for ResonantOS. It can only be issued to wallets with active Community membership.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Community Required</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The program verifies active Community Member status before issuing the licence credential.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">One Per Wallet</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">Duplicate licence credentials are rejected for the same active member record.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Non-Transferable</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-zinc-400">The licence is issued as a soulbound credential, not as a tradable NFT.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Important Distinction</h2>
			<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">
				The old page mixed a broad public licence text with the DAO credential. The current website separates the legal/licence text from the on-chain Symbiotic Licence NFT. The NFT is the verifiable DAO-issued credential; the canonical legal text and hash still need to be finalized before mainnet.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
